---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Design für Alle — Biebrich, Wiesbaden · Madlen von Wulffen"
  description="Co-authored report on inclusive urban planning for the Biebrich district in Wiesbaden, with Büro Grauwert and TU Darmstadt."
>
  <div class="proj-layout">

    <div class="col-images">
      <figure>
        <img src={`${base}images/biebrich-cover.png`} alt="Design für Alle report cover" />
        <figcaption>Design für Alle in der nachhaltigen Stadtentwicklung — report cover. Published by TU Darmstadt & Büro Grauwert, commissioned by Landeshauptstadt Wiesbaden.</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="col-text">
      <div class="text-inner">
        <div class="proj-category">Publication · 2023 – ongoing</div>
        <h1>Inclusive Urban Planning for Biebrich, Wiesbaden</h1>
        <p class="lede">Co-authored report on inclusive urban planning for the Biebrich station district in Wiesbaden — advocating for a value-driven design approach that centers dignity, adaptability, and sustainability.</p>

        <p>In collaboration with Büro Grauwert and TU Darmstadt, I co-authored a report on inclusive urban planning for the Biebrich district in Wiesbaden. Moving beyond deficit-oriented accessibility frameworks, the report advocates for a value-driven design approach that centers dignity, adaptability, and sustainability.</p>
        <p>I shaped the theoretical framework and synthesized relevant case studies, positioning accessibility as an embedded design principle rather than a retrofit.</p>
        <p>This project shaped my understanding of value-driven design frameworks capable of embedding social equity into built environments. It informs my ambition to prototype urban systems that are not only inclusive, but regenerative and future-ready.</p>

        <div class="meta-table">
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Time</span><span class="meta-val">October 2023 – ongoing, Hamburg</span></div>
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Role</span><span class="meta-val">Research Assistant & Co-Author (Mitarbeit)</span></div>
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">With</span><span class="meta-val">Büro Grauwert, TU Darmstadt</span></div>
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Client</span><span class="meta-val">Landeshauptstadt Wiesbaden</span></div>
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Methods</span><span class="meta-val">Literature research, stakeholder analysis, theory synthesis</span></div>
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Read</span><span class="meta-val"><a href="https://tuprints.ulb.tu-darmstadt.de/entities/publication/33cc452e-5a17-4794-a81e-71f5986a2103" target="_blank">Full Report ↗</a></span></div>
        </div>

        <a class="back-link" href={`${base}projects`}>← Back to Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .proj-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; height: calc(100vh - 56px); overflow: hidden; }
  .col-images { height: 100%; overflow-y: scroll; border-right: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0; }
  figure { margin: 0; border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0; }
  figure img { width: 100%; display: block; }
  figcaption { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem 1rem; border-top: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0; }
  .col-text { height: 100%; overflow-y: scroll; }
  .text-inner { padding: 3rem 2.2rem 4rem; }
  .proj-category { font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; text-transform: none; }
  .lede { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.4rem; border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0; padding-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  .col-text p { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.75; color: #2a2a2a; margin-bottom: 1em; }
  h2 { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink); margin: 2rem 0 0.8rem; }
  .meta-table { margin-top: 2.4rem; border-top: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0; padding-top: 1.4rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.7rem; }
  .meta-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr; font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .meta-key { font-size: 0.58rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); padding-top: 0.15rem; }
  .meta-val { font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink); }
  .meta-val a { color: var(--ink); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .back-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 2.4rem; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  :global(body:has(.proj-layout) footer) { display: none; }
  @media (max-width: 860px) { .proj-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; height: auto; overflow: visible; } .col-images, .col-text { height: auto; overflow-y: visible; } .col-images { border-right: none; border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0; } }
</style>
